description: Daniel couldn’t help but gawk at Jack’s muscular physique and touch every muscle on his body. He was amazed at how big he was! Jack was taking it all in with a smile, “He’s making me feel pretty good about myself right now!” Daniel added, “I feel pretty good about yourself!” Then he discovered Jack’s ass, and from there on out it was a matter of when he was going to fuck it and own it.
title: Daniel & Jack: Bareback
